column6: Not only my first time using a mic, later also realizing the uploader and coder was the one who invited me to VRChat worlds later that same first week in VRChat!
A world of helpful tips for VRChat worldmakers! Also one of those first ones Fax showed the newcomer group I was in \o/
Weekly showcases by world makers that I attended my first few months in VRChat, always amazed! (communitymeetup.net)
Monthly showcases by avatar makers that I attended my first few months in VRChat, always amazed! (communitymeetup.net)
So this isn't actually the world I remember seeing in StemVR's Computer Science tour, funny enough... but same creator?
My first time able to recognize some of the names from Community Meetup here!
